### ======================================
### LOURA BACKEND - CORE APP ENDPOINTS
### ======================================
### Base URL for Core: http://localhost:8000/api/core
### Base URL for Auth: http://localhost:8000/api/auth
###
### Instructions:
### 1. Execute Login (in Auth section) to get access/refresh tokens.
### 2. Tokens are stored in variables (VS Code REST Client supports this if configured, 
###    otherwise copy/paste token into @accessToken variable).
### 3. Use these tokens for protected endpoints.
### 4. Run "List Organizations" first to get an Organization ID (@orgId) for other tests.
###
### ======================================

